
Gridded monthly emission changes for the 10 species are given (for months in 2020), based on annual emission grids
These are too big for github, so are on  Zenodo: https://zenodo.org/3854820

Currently mobility-based until previous full month then extrapolated there after, will be updated monthly

Files are absolute changes in  kg substance /m2 /s species
Monthly baselines are the ANNUAL average EDGAR version 5 emission grid for 2015. Our cacluations based in in terms the fractional 
change to baseline, but given in absoulte emission units.


CO2. https://edgar.jrc.ec.europa.eu/gallery.php?release=v50&substance=CO2_excl_short-cycle_org_C&sector=TOTALS 
(2015 data used for consistancy)
CH4 https://edgar.jrc.ec.europa.eu/gallery.php?release=v50&substance=CH4&sector=TOTALS
N2O:https://edgar.jrc.ec.europa.eu/gallery.php?release=v50&substance=N2O&sector=TOTALS

Other species use as baseline of the annual gridmaps, here
https://edgar.jrc.ec.europa.eu/overview.php?v=50_AP 


